description: [``botocore``] This is the initial SDK release for AWS Artifact. AWS Artifact provides on-demand access to compliance and third-party compliance reports. This release includes access to List and Get reports, along with their metadata. This release also includes access to AWS Artifact notifications settings.
[``botocore``] Add ability to override timeout on action level.
[``botocore``] Doc only updates for content enhancement
[``botocore``] Marked fields IpAddressV4, PrivateIpAddress, Email as Sensitive.

[``botocore``] This release adds a new response parameter, JobProgressReport, to the DescribeFHIRImportJob and ListFHIRImportJobs API operation. JobProgressReport provides details on the progress of the import job on the server.
[``botocore``] Amazon Polly adds 1 new voice - Burcu (tr-TR)
[``botocore``] This release adds a new API UpdateClusterSoftware for SageMaker HyperPod. This API allows users to patch HyperPod clusters with latest platform softwares.
[``botocore``] Doc only update for Secrets Manager
[``botocore``] Update endpoint-rules client to latest version
